Package ides.api.plugin.io

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FileIOPlugin
    Interface for plugins which save/load DESModels or which save/load meta-data sections in DESModel files.
    ImportExportPlugin
    Interface for plugins which import/export DESModels.
    IOSubsytem
    Access to loading/saving and import/export of models.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IOPluginManager
    The manager of I/O plugins.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    FileLoadException
    Used when there is a problem loading a file.
    FileSaveException
    Used when there is a problem saving the data in a file.
    FormatTranslationException
    Used when there is a problem during the import or export of a file.
    UnsupportedVersionException
    Used when a file cannot be loaded because the version of the format is not supported.
